    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This car is the perfect canvas for your next automotive adventure. While it's currently in rough shape and will need significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic opportunity to build a vehicle exactly how you want it. If you're looking for a budget-friendly project with plenty of upside potential, this is the one for you!",
